        <mxCell id="note" value="&lt;b&gt;Constraints&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#8226; iOS deployment target: 15.5 (required by google_mlkit_commons)&lt;br&gt;&#8226; ML Kit text recognition is not available on desktop — macOS uses Vision via method channel; Windows / Linux use Tesseract&lt;br&gt;&#8226; camera_desktop image streaming is unavailable on Windows — uses periodic still-frame capture instead&lt;br&gt;&#8226; flutter_zxing is native FFI — barcode decoding cannot be unit-tested; covered by integration tests" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#888888;fillColor=#F5F6F7;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=#0E0E0E;" vertex="1" parent="1">
